Uses of Package
com.cyc.baseclient.kbtool

  • Packages that use com.cyc.baseclient.kbtool 
    Package Description
    com.cyc.baseclient
    Reference implementation of the Base Client API; this code is not supported for external developers.
    com.cyc.baseclient.kbtool
    Classes which wrap common operations for KB content, such as assertion, querying, etc; this code is not supported for external developers.
    com.cyc.query.client.templates  
  • Classes in com.cyc.baseclient.kbtool used by com.cyc.baseclient 
    Class and Description
    AssertToolImpl
    Tools for asserting facts to the Cyc KB.
    ComparisonToolImpl
    Tools for comparing different CycObjects.
    InferenceToolImpl
    Tools for performing inferences over the Cyc KB.
    InspectorToolImpl
    Tools for examining individual CycObjects.
    KbObjectToolImpl
    Provides tools for converting KbObjects to Base Client objects.
    LookupToolImpl
    Tools for looking up CycObjects in the Cyc KB.
    ObjectToolImpl
    Tools for creating simple CycObjects, such as constants and lists.
    UnassertToolImpl
    Tools for unasserting facts from the Cyc KB.
